{"tid":1369091,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日會去元朗行街嘅同我入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-07-26T15:28:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T15:29:50.000Z","uid":241216,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"20add3f02271f712f693b6791333d6061f6c721e","tid":1369091,"uid":241216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:28:43.000Z","msg":"我係元朗人 <br />\n今日行咗成個元朗都見唔到一個垃圾桶<br />\n作為一個有公德心嘅香港人<br />\n梗係有責任保持番呢度乾淨<br />\n我哋梗係唔可以俾人有位入我哋！<br />\n有圖有真相 <br />\n原本擺垃圾筒個位無左垃圾桶<br />\n但係多咗張咁樣嘅橫額<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QP30TbE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQP30TbE.png&h=73674d2d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88c3d2d9ca1933ff9f60f661a6f6a897d4384b68","tid":1369091,"uid":261086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:29:50.000Z","msg":"身在外地既朋友想為大家出一分綿力, 獻上此手繪圖<br />\n請隨意取用及修改<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fLDzPui.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfLDzPui.png&h=98676db3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港，有你有我</span></strong></span>"}]}